  <ability>
    <abilitytitle>Inochian</abilitytitle>
    <abilityid>language.inochian</abilityid>
    <abilityclass>Non-Combat</abilityclass>
    <abilitydescription>
      <p>
	Spoken by the creatures from beyond this plane and the ancients,
	Inochian is a dead language now used only for magic.  It is composed
	of syllables that when intoned resonate with the planes and form
	contagious conduits through which magic may flow.
      </p>
    </abilitydescription>
    

